<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l20"><expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıȷ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Georij </ab>
