<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hartman, uns hat
                            <expan>furg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Jacob Topler,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz ir dem Hansen Hawsell von Seheim,
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> armman, vier pferde
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und im die
                                <expan>widerauszgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, also daz er euch xii
                                <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> dafür
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pürgen</expan> müst. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        sein pürgen, die er euch geseczt hat, ümb <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        xii <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> ledig und lose sagt. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n.</ex></expan> A<expan>ntw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Georii.</ab>
